creator: Kyank Inc
descriptionHtml:
Kyank is connecting Armenians all over the world. Simply download the app and browse through dynamic Armenians looking for a meaningful relationship.



Swipe right on someone you like. If they like you back you will match and get to talk to each other for free. You can use in-app upgrades to match with more Armenians faster



Sign up and start searching for your perfect match!
